
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,360
"Ashes of Love"



00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,240
"Episode 57"



00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:23,180
Mister Immortal,



00:02:23,579 --> 00:02:24,540
here is the wedding invitation
card from Demon Realm.



