00:02:40,170 --> 00:02:41,730
he grew up from a little baby



00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:43,770
and became such a demon.



00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,260
Even though he is the Demon Lord now,



00:02:46,750 --> 00:02:48,130
it can’t be denied that he is my nephew.



00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,440
