00:02:50,930 --> 00:02:52,310
I will teach him a lesson



00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,550
when I meet him.



00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:01,330
Xu Feng.



00:03:03,770 --> 00:03:04,660
Xu Feng,



00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,130
Nether Fury appears in the Wangchuan River.



00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:07,280
I’m afraid that Mi Ci is in danger.



00:03:07,730 --> 00:03:08,710
Nether Fury?



00:03:08,970 --> 00:03:11,370
Someone must be forcing Mu Ci
to make Spirit-Vanishing Arrow.



00:03:11,770 --> 00:03:12,750
With his health condition,



00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,950
he can't bear it at all.



00:03:14,130 --> 00:03:15,060
And I’m also worried that



00:03:15,370 --> 00:03:17,370
the Spirit-Vanishing Arrow will be used to kill you.



00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:20,170
Is it King of Gu City?



00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,040
Xu Feng



00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,930
My Lord. He...



00:03:26,930 --> 00:03:27,820
You may go.



00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,660
Yes, my Lord.



00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:30,800
Uncle.



00:03:31,329 --> 00:03:32,660
Do you still regard me as your uncle?



00:03:33,820 --> 00:03:34,930
You must be joking, uncle.



00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,040
Due to fatigue, you have got
two big dark circles under your eyes .



00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:43,150
I received the wedding invitation card,
which shows that you are going to marry Sui He.



00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,350
It is not true, is it?



00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,910
It’s true indeed.



00:03:46,170 --> 00:03:48,130
Uncle, I hope you will come here
to preside over the wedding ceremony for me.



00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:49,240
Xu Feng,



00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,550
how come you have been so muddle-headed
since you became Demon Lord?



00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,079
Why are you going to marry Sui He, that evil witch?



00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:56,400
Do you know how much Jin Mi sacrificed



00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,730
in order to bring you back to life?



00:03:57,730 --> 00:03:58,400
You must be joking, uncle.



00:03:58,930 --> 00:03:59,910
The one who saved me



00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,280
is Sui He.



00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:04,400
Sui He did manage to take away the phoenix hairpin



00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,510
and save one piece of your soul.



00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,880
But the thing that brought you back to life



00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:09,110
was the Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir
that Jin Mi made efforts to get.



00:04:09,420 --> 00:04:12,400
In order to get Light of Xuangqiong,
the guiding medicine of the Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir



00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:15,200
Jin Mi risked her life to climb the Snake Mountain.



00:04:15,370 --> 00:04:16,970
She almost lost her life.



00:04:17,370 --> 00:04:18,440
Do you know this?



00:04:19,370 --> 00:04:20,350
It surprises me that



00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,970
Water Immortal is extremely good at



00:04:22,970 --> 00:04:24,040
befogging people’s minds.



00:04:24,660 --> 00:04:26,480
She and Run Yu worked in collusion,



00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:28,220
having me under their complete control.



00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,880
Uncle, you also saw that



00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,170
she killed me with one stab.



00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:35,110
How come you are bewitched by her now?



00:04:35,420 --> 00:04:37,110
Can’t you see her true colors?



00:04:37,330 --> 00:04:39,600
You don’t even believe me.



00:04:40,350 --> 00:04:41,180
Jin Mi was wrong.



00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:42,140
She did kill you.



00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:44,620
I don’t intend to argue for her.



00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:46,480
But in order to make up for this,



00:04:46,659 --> 00:04:48,350
Jin Mi managed to get the Golden Elixir.



00:04:49,550 --> 00:04:50,880
She risked her life many times



00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,400
and almost lost her life.



00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,220
I witnessed all these happenings.



00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:55,950
Uncle, it seems that you are here



00:04:55,950 --> 00:04:57,240
not to see me,



00:04:58,170 --> 00:04:59,950
but to argue for Water Immortal.



00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:03,020
If so,



00:05:03,020 --> 00:05:05,640
don’t bother anymore.



00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,420
-No matter what Water Immortal did,
-You—



00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,020
it has nothing to do with me.



00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:12,440
The moment she stabbed me in the back,



00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:14,530
all the connections between us were broken.



00:05:15,150 --> 00:05:16,130
Sui He is



00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,640
the future Demon Empress I’m going to marry.



00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:20,930
Form now on, I will only



00:05:21,770 --> 00:05:22,800
care about her.



00:05:23,770 --> 00:05:24,530
You



00:05:25,110 --> 00:05:25,950
are so muddle-headed.



00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:27,820
Sui He is the murderer



00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:29,510
who killed Luo Lin and Lin Xiu.



00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:30,710
-Listen to me.
-Uncle,



00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,150
I have something important to do today.



00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:36,350
I have no time to talk about the past.



00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,970
I have decided on this marriage.



00:05:39,150 --> 00:05:40,130
Uncle, please don’t try to persuade me anymore.



00:05:41,110 --> 00:05:42,260
If you don’t want to



00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:43,460
preside over the wedding ceremony for me,



00:05:44,170 --> 00:05:45,420
I won’t force you.



00:05:46,930 --> 00:05:47,510
See you.



00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:48,750
You—



00:06:09,910 --> 00:06:10,530
Search this place.



00:06:10,660 --> 00:06:11,460
Yes, my Lord.



00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:17,510
Xu Feng, you didn’t say anything along the way.



00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:19,280
You must feel bad. Right?



00:06:20,930 --> 00:06:23,060
She made my uncle speak for her,



00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:25,860
alienating me from Sui He.



00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:27,370
She has exhausted her tricks.



00:06:29,150 --> 00:06:31,020
Moon Immortal is not a nose of wax.



00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:32,800
So he can’t go so far as to be made use of by others.



00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:35,280
Maybe there are some hidden facts in this matter.



00:06:36,970 --> 00:06:38,440
You also believe what my uncle said.



00:06:39,370 --> 00:06:40,530
To put it in an offensive way,



00:06:41,110 --> 00:06:42,530
between Sui He and Jin Mi,



00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:43,510
I would like to believe



00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:45,020
Sui He is the murderer.



00:06:47,150 --> 00:06:48,260
Xu Feng, you are



00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:50,130
afraid that you don’t know how to treat Jin Mi



00:06:50,130 --> 00:06:51,640
if she is really the person who saved your life. Right?



00:06:55,820 --> 00:06:56,970
I am afraid that



00:06:58,170 --> 00:07:00,040
what Jin Mi said is true.



00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,510
What did she say?



00:07:01,770 --> 00:07:03,200
You didn’t kill my daddy.



00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,060
I got you wrong.



00:07:05,370 --> 00:07:06,620
At that time, all the evidences,



00:07:07,020 --> 00:07:08,880
All the evidences showed that you were the murderer.



00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:10,800
I had no choice but to believe it, phoenix.



00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,170
Half an year later, when I woke up,



00:07:12,170 --> 00:07:13,730
I found that someone had cheated in those evidences.



00:07:13,730 --> 00:07:15,420
But it was too late at the time.



00:07:15,420 --> 00:07:17,060
It’s her who killed my daddy.



00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:18,000
It’s Sui He



00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:20,080
Sui He can use Glazed Pure Fire.



00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,150
She framed you.



00:07:21,150 --> 00:07:23,200
I went to take the Internal Dan of Jiu Ying



00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,350
for Lord Puchi.



00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:26,170
He was injured because of Sui He.



00:07:26,170 --> 00:07:28,400
It was Sui He who hurt him with Liuli Fire.



00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,260
If without the comparison today,



00:07:31,910 --> 00:07:33,460
I wouldn’t realize



00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:35,909
how precious Sui He is to me.



00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:38,440
Sui He is not the kind of person you think.



00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:40,800
She is not the kind of person she appears to be.



00:07:41,150 --> 00:07:42,800
She admitted to me



00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:45,150
that she killed my dad and shifted the blame on you.



00:07:45,150 --> 00:07:46,260
She is the culprit.



00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:47,420
She’s wicked.



00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:49,240
She is not the kind of person she appears to be.



00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,480
Phoenix, I beg you. Please believe me.



00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,620
I don't want her to stay with you.



00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:54,480
I don't want her to hurt you again.



00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,060
Phoenix.



00:07:58,310 --> 00:08:00,400
She said the murderer who killed
Water Immortal and Wind Immortal



00:08:01,510 --> 00:08:02,130
is Sui He.



00:08:02,930 --> 00:08:03,950
Sui He?



00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,060
Can she use Glazed Pure Fire?



00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,200
I don’t know, either.



00:08:09,820 --> 00:08:11,370
But she did consume a lot of magic power



00:08:11,820 --> 00:08:13,200
when she tried to bring me back to life.



00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,930
Since I woke up,



00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,970
she has always been very weak.



00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:20,080
My Lord, we haven’t found Mu Ci.



00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:24,440
Let's look for him separately.



00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:28,350
Xu Feng, if you find Mu Ci,



00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:30,260
no matter what he says and what he does,



00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,260
no matter he is alive or dead,



00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,350
take him over to see me.



00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,440
OK.



00:08:38,659 --> 00:08:39,510
Let’s go.



00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,820
What's wrong with me?



00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,040
Liu Ying.



00:09:44,260 --> 00:09:45,240
The sixth day of the sixth lunar month.



00:09:46,530 --> 00:09:47,680
The place where we
expressed our affection to each other.



00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,040
Your Highness.



00:10:03,950 --> 00:10:04,660
Mu Ci,



00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:07,200
King of Gu City let me take the Spirit-Vanishing Arrow.



00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,750
Did he hurt you?



00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,570
If you don’t give him Spirit-Vanishing Arrow,



00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:14,750
he will kill me.



00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:29,200
The sixth day of the sixth lunar month?



00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:35,640
Give me the Spirit-Vanishing Arrow first.



00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:37,370
Let's leave here first, okay?



00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:39,370
OK.



00:10:49,820 --> 00:10:51,680
Xu Feng, did you find any clues?



00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,660
Keep looking for him.



00:10:58,930 --> 00:10:59,730
Yes, my Lord.



00:11:02,930 --> 00:11:04,350
Tomorrow is the sixth day of the sixth lunar month.



00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:06,930
He promised me



00:11:07,860 --> 00:11:09,110
that he would marry me.



00:11:27,550 --> 00:11:28,440
Any clues?



00:11:40,530 --> 00:11:42,400
It seems that someone used magic
to create a protection ward here.



00:11:43,950 --> 00:11:45,730
It’s very likely that Mu Ci
is trapped somewhere nearby.



00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:02,400
You stay here. I am going to have a look first.



00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,860
No, let’s go together.



00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:06,080
Let’s go.



00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:36,750
Mu Ci.



00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:38,710
It's him.



00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:40,260
He has been here.



00:12:40,570 --> 00:12:41,950
Did Mu Ci kill King of Gu City?



00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,400
Then he must be around here.



00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:45,280
Yes.



00:12:46,930 --> 00:12:47,950
He must be alive.



00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:49,420
He must be alive.



00:12:49,420 --> 00:12:50,040
Let’s go.



00:12:57,730 --> 00:12:58,930
The sixth day of the sixth lunar month.



00:13:00,350 --> 00:13:01,370
The place where we
expressed our affection to each other.



00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:03,510
The sixth day of the sixth lunar month.



00:13:17,460 --> 00:13:19,550
In such a condition,



00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:20,660
do you think you can kill me?



00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:23,860
As the King of Gu City,



00:13:24,530 --> 00:13:26,000
don’t you know that



00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:28,780
one will be dead



00:13:28,780 --> 00:13:33,770
even if he just got a little wound
caused by Spirit-Vanishing Arrow?



00:14:25,110 --> 00:14:26,260
Liu Ying,



00:14:27,060 --> 00:14:28,440
I will keep my promise.



00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:11,820
The news about Xu Feng’ s wedding
has already been proclaimed in the six realms.



00:15:16,310 --> 00:15:17,950
Can't you still let go of him?



00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:19,240
Yes.



00:15:21,950 --> 00:15:23,600
He is gonna get married



00:15:24,310 --> 00:15:25,770
and become someone else’ s groom.



00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:41,950
Mi, your hands are so cold.



00:15:41,950 --> 00:15:43,060
Let's go back.



00:15:46,660 --> 00:15:47,640
It seems that



00:15:48,570 --> 00:15:50,440
every time when I feel cold,



00:15:51,420 --> 00:15:53,020
you always give me warmth.



00:15:53,770 --> 00:15:55,680
That's because I’m afraid of coldness, too.



00:15:58,570 --> 00:15:59,510
Mi,



00:16:00,310 --> 00:16:02,480
if two cold people stay together,



00:16:03,330 --> 00:16:05,110
at lease they can give warmth to each other.



00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:07,060
And they won’t hurt each other.



00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,840
But



00:16:09,950 --> 00:16:11,200
the winter snow and summer sun



00:16:11,460 --> 00:16:13,150
are destined to be incompatible.



00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:29,550
The snow of Human Realm has melted.



00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,040
On the fifteenth day of the next lunar month,



00:16:32,570 --> 00:16:34,840
the first flower of spring will bloom.



00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:38,000
It’s really an auspicious day for wedding.



00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:40,930
Then let's hold our wedding on that day.



00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:45,510
Mi,



00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:47,770
what did you say?



00:16:53,150 --> 00:16:54,400
You said



00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:56,400
that day is an auspicious day.



00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:58,840
Then let's hold our wedding on that day.



00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:05,280
Mi,



00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,369
are you serious?



00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:16,220
Mi.



00:17:26,710 --> 00:17:27,950
It’s OK that we don’t love each other fervently,



00:17:27,950 --> 00:17:29,420
as long as we can be together forever.



00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:32,040
Let me be by your side,



00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:34,000
and I’ll be satisfied.



00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:36,080
Among the three of us,



00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:38,400
two persons can be happy,



00:17:38,970 --> 00:17:40,620
which is sort of a satisfactory result.



00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:02,710
Your Majesty.



00:18:12,530 --> 00:18:13,280
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.



00:18:13,460 --> 00:18:14,080
I was careless.



00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:16,480
Stand up first.



00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:21,770
Kuang Lu,



00:18:22,710 --> 00:18:23,730
do you know that?



00:18:24,170 --> 00:18:25,770
She finally agrees to marry me.



00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,600
I didn’t expect that



00:18:30,220 --> 00:18:32,080
she would agree without any hesitation.



00:18:34,570 --> 00:18:35,910
That’s great.



00:18:35,910 --> 00:18:37,240
Congratulations, Your Majesty.



00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:41,730
On which day



00:18:42,620 --> 00:18:44,170
will the wedding ceremony be hold?



00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:45,680
On the fifteenth day of the next lunar month.



00:18:47,150 --> 00:18:48,880
Then let me prepare for it.



00:18:49,150 --> 00:18:50,620
You have been very tired these days.



00:18:51,110 --> 00:18:52,440
I’ll let others prepare for it.



00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:56,480
Your Majesty, you had this wish



00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:57,510
when you were a prince.



00:18:58,080 --> 00:18:59,640
Now your wish is fulfilled.



00:18:59,950 --> 00:19:01,330
I’m very happy, too.



00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:03,150
I want to get some lucks
by involving in this joyous event.



00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:05,330
OK, then as you wish.



00:19:47,910 --> 00:19:48,930
I’m Kuang Lu, a soldier of Heaven Realm.



00:19:48,930 --> 00:19:49,860
I’m here to report my arrival to you, Night Immortal.



00:19:49,860 --> 00:19:52,000
Few people work in my Xuanji Palace,
and there are much chores to do.



00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,330
You can ask me to do anything.



00:19:53,330 --> 00:19:55,020
I have to get up early and stay up late at night.
And I work on night shifts.



00:19:55,020 --> 00:19:56,040
I can do it.



00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:56,880
I’m bad-tempered.



00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:58,480
I hurt people occasionally.



00:19:58,880 --> 00:20:01,280
I just want to follow you, Your Highness.



00:20:02,170 --> 00:20:03,460
In these thousands of years,



00:20:03,460 --> 00:20:05,020
no one has stood the test.



00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:06,660
All of them have been fired by me.



00:20:07,550 --> 00:20:08,750
But I have never thought about



00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:09,510
betraying you, Your Highness.



00:20:09,820 --> 00:20:11,200
Trust me, Your Highness.



00:20:12,930 --> 00:20:14,400
I hope that you



00:20:14,710 --> 00:20:16,530
will trust me the way
you trust Beast of Dreams from now on.



